--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTE4MQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/buzzfeed_articles_778/e56c2f92f3e3836d3c0b7a0016b281b2\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdialog aria-label=\"Modal Dialog\" aria-modal=\"true\"\u003e\u003c/dialog\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e @Mike_Pence / Via \u003ca href=\"https://go.redirectingat.com/?id=74679X1524629\u0026amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.buzzfeed.com%2Fmichaelabramwell%2Freactions-trumps-tweet-about-law-violation\u0026amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FMike_Pence%2Fstatus%2F1890887398461948057\u0026amp;xcust=7831589%7C0%7CRSS%7C0\u0026amp;xs=1\" data-i13n=\"elm:affiliate_link;elmt:premonetized\" rel=\"sponsored\" target=\"_blank\" data-ylk=\"slk:x.com;elm:affiliate_link;elmt:premonetized;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\"\u003ex.com\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eHere\u0026#39;s a brief \u003ca href=\"https://go.redirectingat.com/?id=74679X1524629\u0026amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.buzzfeed.com%2Fmichaelabramwell%2Freactions-trumps-tweet-about-law-violation\u0026amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fimprimis.hillsdale.edu%2Fthe-presidency-and-the-constitution%2F\u0026amp;xcust=7831589%7C0%7CRSS%7C0\u0026amp;xs=1\" data-i13n=\"elm:affiliate_link;elmt:premonetized\" rel=\"sponsored\" target=\"_blank\" data-ylk=\"slk:excerpt:;elm:affiliate_link;elmt:premonetized;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\"\u003eexcerpt:\u003c/a\u003e \u0026#34;The president is not our teacher, our tutor, our guide or ruler. He does not command us; we command him. We serve neither him nor his vision.\u0026#34;\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"Text excerpt discussing the president\u0026amp;#39;s role, suggesting they do not command or redefine customs, law, or beliefs, nor impose decisions on the people\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"960\" height=\"821\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/